headline: Paychex, Inc. Schedules Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings Conference Call for December 19, 2024
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., December 05, 2024--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) will release financial results for its fiscal 2025 second quarter ended November 30, 2024. Paychex will deliver results via Business Wire before the financial markets open on Thursday, December 19, 2024.
